      "content": "i'm not really worried about potassium or anything, i've been on this for ages and i'm fine. my main concern is just the gap in my dosage. if i take them both now, it just gets me back on my regular schedule, right? i'd rather just get the full amount in my system now than deal with a spike later tonight or tomorrow morning. it seems safer to just stay consistent with the 20mg levels. what do you think?",
